'''小约翰·威廉·尼科尔森'''（{{lang-en|'''John William Nicholson, Jr.'''}}，{{bd|1957年|5月8日|||catIdx=H}}），[[美国陆军|美国陆军]][[上将_(美国)|上将]]，现为[[坚定支援任务|坚定支援任务]]司令兼驻阿美军司令，之前担任盟军陆军司令部司令。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aco.nato.int/change-of-command-at-natos-allied-land-command.aspx |title=Change of Command at NATO's Allied Land Command |author=SHAPE Public Affairs Office |website=Allied Command Operations |publisher=NATO |access-date=1 June 2015 |archive-date=2015-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150329215028/http://www.aco.nato.int/change-of-command-at-natos-allied-land-command.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>还曾担任[[第82空降师|第82空降师]]师长，他的父亲约翰·尼科尔森也曾在美国陆军服役，军衔至少将。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.dvidshub.net/image/1359955/all-american-week-international-day-and-paratroopers-ball#.VWy0d9JVhBd |title=Images: All American Week International Day and Paratroopers Ball [Image 1 of 8] |author=Nguyen Christophe |date=22 May 2014 |website=Defense Video and Imagery Distribution System |access-date=1 June 2015 |quote=Brig. Gen. John W. Nicholson Sr. (right) and Norine MacDonald, wife of Maj. Gen. John W. Nicholson Jr., commander of the 82nd Airborne Division, share a dance at the All American Week International Paratroopers Ball, May 21, 2014. |archive-date=2016-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413071938/https://www.dvidshub.net/image/1359955/all-american-week-international-day-and-paratroopers-ball#.VWy0d9JVhBd |dead-url=no }}<br/>{{cite book|title=Register of Graduates and Former Cadets of the United States Military Academy|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=xXreAAAAMAAJ|year=1991|publisher=Association of Graduates, USMA.}}</ref> 他们是英国准将约翰·尼科尔森的远房亲戚。<ref>{{cite book|author=Carlotta Gall|authorlink=Carlotta Gall|title=The Wrong Enemy: America in Afghanistan, 2001–2014|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Rd9JAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA115|date=8 April 2014|publisher=Houghton Mifflin Harcourt|isbn=978-0-544-04568-2|page=115}}</ref> 2016年2月4日，尼科尔森晋升上将的提名获得通过，3月2日，正式晋升上将，接替[[约翰·坎贝尔_(美军上将)|约翰·坎贝尔]]陆军上将，担任坚定支援任务司令兼驻阿美军司令。

